{"tid":922731,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[NS] [3DS] [PKM] USUM & LPLE 討論區 #23 Switch陣亡 2019見","createTime":"2018-11-30T15:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T15:37:34.000Z","uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"10e6fac98f6a6cdff08cbc489ee5c2cf0c62ac1d","tid":922731,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:33:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZKk0jO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZKk0jO.gif&h=5166ed2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dGw3HEi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdGw3HEi.png&h=4a3ad4ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此POST並非小圈子<br />\n<br />\n嚴禁召開TG進行小圈子活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n禁止討論修改及盜版遊戲<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請支持官方授權<br />\n<br />\n香港Pok&eacute;mon比賽</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://playpokemonhk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplaypokemonhk.com%2F&d=SNbqRTYp6WmwN%2BJiJDvjey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=210b85c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://playpokemonhk.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PlayPokemonHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPlayPokemonHK%2F&d=SNbqRTYp6WmwN%2BJiJDvjey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=bb9f22cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PlayPokemonHK/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">Q&amp;A</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>0. 皮卡丘伊布胡地肯泰羅卡蒂狗凱羅斯快龍拉普拉斯超夢我想知呢...</strong><br />\n冇人識你依堆咩黎 想討論唔該用返<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港式譯名</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://n1.hkgpkm.pw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn1.hkgpkm.pw&d=SNbqRTYp6WmwN%2BJiJDvjey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5c5f47fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://n1.hkgpkm.pw</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://n2.hkgpkm.pw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hkgpkm.pw&d=SNbqRTYp6WmwN%2BJiJDvjey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=e78b49e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://n2.hkgpkm.pw</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 我買日版遊戲會唔會有中文？</strong><br />\n買咩版都有齊九國語言<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 點解刷極都係女比卡超/伊貝既？我想要仔</strong><br />\n性別係開game一刻就鎖定左 要刷就要由頭玩過<br />\n性格就可以係研究所前面save再刷<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 夢夢點拎？有無得刷性格？</strong><br />\n一粒pokeball一隻夢夢 無得刷得一次機會 想刷買多幾粒波<br />\n<br />\n<strong>4. 各種精靈咩性格好？</strong><br />\nPartner比卡超：naive/hasty<br />\nPartner伊貝： adamant, modest, 對人戰亦可考慮加防/特防性格<br />\n夢夢(冇得刷)： 好多性格都得 但做攻手唔夠超夢夢/富迪爭 刷Bold當盾都唔錯<br />\nLIHKG LPLE Nature Recommendation<br />\n<a href=\"http://lgnr.hkgpkm.pw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flgnr.hkgpkm.pw%2F&d=SNbqRTYp6WmwN%2BJiJDvjey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=79b4613b\" target=\"_blank\">http://lgnr.hkgpkm.pw/</a><br />\n<br />\n性格表google下就會有 <span style=\"color: red;\">*如果過關爆機就棄game的話其實冇必要刷*</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>4. 熱門精靈係邊度捉？</strong><br />\n奇異種子：常青森林<br />\n小火龍：3號道路<br />\n車厘龜：25,26號道路<br />\n迷你龍：中大  <del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">發電廠條水路</span></span></del><br />\n化石飛龍：化石博物館拎琥珀 去紅蓮島研究所復活<br />\n識英文請睇 <a href=\"https://www.serebii.net/pokedex-sm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.serebii.net%2Fpokedex-sm%2F&d=SNbqRTYp6WmwN%2BJiJDvjey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=b9912a32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.serebii.net/pokedex-sm/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>5. 咩係連鎖？</strong><br />\n淨係撞同一隻，狂捉<br />\n中間唔可以遇其他寵<br />\n如果遇左其他寵走佬就得<br />\n即係連續30場捉同一隻全部捉晒<br />\n30有機會出6V 同提高出色違機率<br />\n<br />\n<strong>6. 邊度Check 6V or iv值? 咩係6V？</strong><br />\nCheck V 地點: 11號道路通道上層博士<br />\n首先11號道路通道上層博士的助手度拎到Check功能<br />\n拎到之後係自己pkm度按Y制黎check<br />\n<br />\nV係指單項個體值最高(31), 6V就係6項個體值皆最高<br />\n留意6V唔代表最完美 特攻型精靈應該刷5V 0攻<br />\n<br />\n<strong>7. 粒波點熄聲？</strong><br />\n中間粒制同頂制 兩個制一齊禁<br />\n入左精靈之後，長按粒的，之後變左精靈隻色再即刻按頂果粒制，會即刻震，就ok<br />\n可能要拎左夢夢先熄得聲<br />\n<br />\n<strong>8. 點先拎到忍蛙居合斬/飛天多多利/滑浪比卡超/莎菲亞怪力/閃光超能貓？</strong><br />\nKeyword<br />\n居合斬 - 遊輪<br />\n飛天 - 遊戲機中心門口<br />\n滑浪 - 淺紅市<br />\n怪力 - 金牙 淺紅市NPC<br />\n閃光 - 地鼠山洞 深灰市<br />\n<br />\n<strong>9. 點進太陽伊貝月伊貝大鋼蛇巨鉗螳螂....？</strong><br />\nLPLE不存在的精靈一覽：<br />\n<a href=\"https://serebii.net/letsgopikachueevee/kantopokedex.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fserebii.net%2Fletsgopikachueevee%2Fkantopokedex.shtml&d=SNbqRTYp6WmwN%2BJiJDvjey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=d671fa70\" target=\"_blank\">https://serebii.net/letsgopikachueevee/kantopokedex.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>10. 我想online同人交換進化富迪/恥鬼/滾動岩/怪力，又或者同人對戰，要點做？</strong><br />\n課金先可以online，面連係唔洗俾錢<br />\n<br />\n<strong>11. 我想問依隻寵應該配邊四招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n每隻PKM都有唔同玩法 請你講清楚你想點玩先好問配招<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>12. 我隻超能貓唔小心忘記左招光牆 想問點學返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </strong><br />\n聯盟PC有個呀婆比你回憶技能<br />\n心之鱗片可以係每日隨機道具執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>13. 點解我騎騎下飛行寵會飛高左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我畏高點落返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </strong><br />\n今代特色 比你可以捉天空上面既寵<br />\n收返隻寵就可以落地 無快捷鍵 垃圾GF<br />\n<br />\n<strong>14. 點解我上網連線打黎打去對面D戰術一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n因為今代GF刪左太多技搞到對戰單一化<br />\n有興趣研究對戰既話歡迎加入USUM懷抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>15. 點解我問野無人應我 依個POST係咪小圈子 </strong><br />\n你自己反省下有無講過官譯或者留TG<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a76b2a6a636e6d846b6d7593b3cbb089b1d47a","tid":922731,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:33:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">爆機後資料</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">其他資料(待整理)</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a84508a34c8bea4a57c48ed2056639ff3b12e7a","tid":922731,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>參考網站(USUM資訊)</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n培育入門<span style=\"color: red;\">(新手必睇)</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tut1.hkgpkm.pw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftut1.hkgpkm.pw&d=SNbqRTYp6WmwN%2BJiJDvjey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=3604b908\" target=\"_blank\">http://tut1.hkgpkm.pw</a><br />\n<br />\n傷害計算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pokemon-trainer.net/sm/dmcs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpokemon-trainer.net%2Fsm%2Fdmcs%2F&d=SNbqRTYp6WmwN%2BJiJDvjey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=49b6f5a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://pokemon-trainer.net/sm/dmcs/</a> (日)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pokemonshowdown.com/damagecalc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpokemonshowdown.com%2Fdamagecalc%2F&d=SNbqRTYp6WmwN%2BJiJDvjey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=a6fd394f\" target=\"_blank\">https://pokemonshowdown.com/damagecalc/</a> (英)<br />\n<br />\n個體計算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.serebii.net/games/iv-calcsm.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.serebii.net%2Fgames%2Fiv-calcsm.shtml&d=SNbqRTYp6WmwN%2BJiJDvjey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=efc88023\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.serebii.net/games/iv-calcsm.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n最大耐久指數計算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://pkc.client.jp/w/defmax.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpkc.client.jp%2Fw%2Fdefmax.html&d=SNbqRTYp6WmwN%2BJiJDvjey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=aef7d800\" target=\"_blank\">http://pkc.client.jp/w/defmax.html</a> (日)<br />\n<br />\n圖鑑/資料網站<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://serebii.net/pokedex-sm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fserebii.net%2Fpokedex-sm%2F&d=SNbqRTYp6WmwN%2BJiJDvjey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=b012e21f\" target=\"_blank\">http://serebii.net/pokedex-sm/</a> (英)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bokevon.web.fc2.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbokevon.web.fc2.com%2F&d=SNbqRTYp6WmwN%2BJiJDvjey7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=c90f9b48\" target=\"_blank\">http://bokevon.web.fc2.com/</a> (英日中)"},{"pid":"57d8e04b33a52bc4caa0aeee4edd1132da6a5dde","tid":922731,"uid":82231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:34:05.000Z","msg":"負皮"},{"pid":"365653885c4305fb7eeebc944f4bfe53984ff3d1","tid":922731,"uid":34243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"Topic真係加usum？唔洗啦"},{"pid":"0781fcaa86a1d24682ad4499264a862d39286337","tid":922731,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"365653885c4305fb7eeebc944f4bfe53984ff3d1","tid":922731,"uid":34243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"Topic真係加usum？唔洗啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你下個POST改返囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcfbf4d8b3f7c34afc5f0cc07afae474075bfc07","tid":922731,"uid":82231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"下個post標題<br />\n應該係 pkm陣亡"},{"pid":"ab77ca7f03a5f28f5b155642e38239fd1240dbcd","tid":922731,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"